name: Origami hOHM
reason:
[hOHM](https://origami.finance/collections/olympus-collection/1-0x1DB1591540d7A6062Be0837ca3C808aDd28844F6/info) is a tokenized `levered OHM` vault created by [Origami Finance](https://x.com/origami_fi).

It has consistently maintained a TVL > $105 million. This is over one third of the entire gOHM (governance OHM) supply.

There is an LP position in uniswap, which Barter and others route in their solver.
